Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Import errors between modules

Solution: Ensure all scripts are in correct directories and use proper import paths
Issue: JSON file errors

Solution: Check that directories exist before writing files; use os.makedirs(dirname, exist_ok=True)
Issue: Date formatting issues

Solution: Use consistent date format (YYYY-MM-DD) and datetime.strptime() for parsing
Issue: Template variables not substituting

Solution: Verify all template variables in format strings match the kwargs passed to format()
